div.p: Fife Public Schools aspires to be a top tier learning organization in which all students are being prepared for college, career, and life. The mission of Fife Public Schools is to provide an engaging and safe environment where learning is linked to life. The vision of Fife Public Schools is to develop students who are caring and compassionate, prepared for life's challenges and accountable for their actions and the betterment of society.
